  "synopsis": "The pathfinder searches for the \"path\" that grants wishes. It's great that Garam, an ordinary student leaves the world with impulsive thoughts but, When she comes back, the world became a ghost town where all the people and animals have disappeared.\n\nTo find her family and have the world back the way it was, she must find a “path”\n\nYou could be swept away by an avalanche in the mountains, Deep seas where it is difficult to breath, hellish labyrinths, and more.\n\nThis is a series of hardships to find the paths that are in dangerous places.\n\n(Source: Kakao, translated)",
